Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.40,0:01:35.74,Title,,0,0,0,,{\i1\pos(704.063,582.5)}The Light & Dark\N{\i1}of the Mangekyo Sharingan{\i0}\N\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.59,0:01:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You've become...strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.35,0:01:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The same line as before...\Nand the bird...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.89,0:02:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Another farce with\Nyour special genjutsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.73,0:02:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.31,0:02:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not over,\Nbut I'll hear you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.65,0:02:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll say it once more...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.04,0:02:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,When you killed off the entire clan,\N you mentioned the existence of another person.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.38,0:02:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So that Uchiha member you didn't kill\Nwas a co-conspirator.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.51,0:02:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Even you could not kill\Nthe entire Police Force alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.60,0:02:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So you figured it out...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.68,0:02:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.44,0:02:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Madara Uchiha...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.93,0:03:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With that vision and chakra\N{\i1}more ominous than my own...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.38,0:03:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's just like...Madara Uchiha,\N{\i1}from long ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.36,0:03:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hell if I know...that person.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.01,0:03:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Madara...Uchiha?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.43,0:03:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,One of the founders\Nof Hidden Leaf Village...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.81,0:03:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The man who first possessed\Nthe Mangekyo Sharingan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.43,0:03:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Founder?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.52,0:03:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That Madara\Nshould be long dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.69,0:03:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you making fun of me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.45,0:03:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Madara is alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.95,0:03:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's up to you whether you believe\Nthat or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.14,0:03:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop joking around!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.16,0:03:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to survive, we cling to\Nall we know and understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.42,0:03:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And we label it reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.97,0:04:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But knowledge and understanding\Nare ambiguous.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.93,0:04:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That reality could be an illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.22,0:04:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,All humans live with\Nthe wrong assumptions.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.81,0:04:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that another way\Nof looking at it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.27,0:04:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Just what are you trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.46,0:04:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only your assumption\Nthat Madara is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.03,0:04:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,In exactly the same way you once assumed\N that I was your kind older brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.00,0:04:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I just pretended to be the kind\Nof brother you wanted...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.66,0:04:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,in order to measure your vessel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.76,0:04:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened that night...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.08,0:04:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I was so young and thought\Nit was all an illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.03,0:05:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That I was caught in\Na cruel genjutsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.69,0:05:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to believe that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.84,0:05:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But that was...unmistakably reality!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.08,0:05:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,My eye is not like it was\Nin the past!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.90,0:05:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,My Sharingan can see\Nthrough genjutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.47,0:05:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You still speak with such confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.68,0:05:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But for now, I'll take your word for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.63,0:05:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we end this little charade?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.45,0:05:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Being confident is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.49,0:05:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But Sasuke, your eye still isn't\Nthe same as mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.37,0:05:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then one day, come before me with\N{\i1}the same eye that I possess.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.46,0:05:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,So...you couldn't kill the friend\Nwho is most dear to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.92,0:06:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And you dared to appear before me\Nwith such weak resolve?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.75,0:06:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Then hurry it up and try to kill me\Nwith your Mangekyo Sharingan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.69,0:06:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Or is it too difficult to test\Nyour capability against me now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.40,0:06:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You're pretty sure of yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.78,0:06:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Neither of them has moved\Nfor a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.40,0:06:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,They're just feeling each other out\Nwith genjutsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.67,0:06:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Mangekyo Sharingan...\NThis eye is special...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.39,0:06:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,From the moment it awakens,\Nit goes towards the dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.89,0:06:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And the more it is used,\Nthe more it is sealed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.53,0:06:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.46,0:06:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,In time, the Mangekyo Sharingan\Nloses its light.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.22,0:06:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Blindness...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.15,0:07:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that the trade-off for the power\Nto control the Nine-Tails?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.94,0:07:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You did as I instructed and read\N the lithograph in the meeting room?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.16,0:07:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Madara... Exactly who and what is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.47,0:07:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The first one ever to use that eye\Nto tame the Nine-Tails.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.88,0:07:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,An immortal man who is both\Nmy partner and my mentor...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.09,0:07:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And the only one to uncover the\N other secret of the Mangekyo Sharingan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.47,0:07:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That...is Madara Uchiha.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.10,0:07:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The other secret of\NMangekyo Sharingan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.78,0:07:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It has another ocular power aside\Nfrom taming the Nine-Tails?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.71,0:08:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... One more secret.\NThe most important secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.96,0:08:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Most important secret?\NWhat is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.05,0:08:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?! Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.64,0:08:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me tell you a little\Nabout the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.48,0:08:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It concerns the history\Nof the Uchiha.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.48,0:08:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Long ago, Madara had a brother...\NA younger brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.50,0:08:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Madara Uchiha and\Nhis younger brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.50,0:08:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,From the time they were little,\N they honed their skills and competed with each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.43,0:08:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The Mangekyo Sharingan awakened in them both...\N and in time, they were considered special by their clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.48,0:09:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Both sought to sharpen their ocular\N powers and competed against each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.99,0:09:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And the brothers...\N They killed off those important to them
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.68,0:09:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,and finally awakened\Nthe Mangekyo Sharingan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.42,0:09:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It had never before been seen\Namong the Uchiha.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.51,0:09:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The brothers used their ocular powers to\N take control and Madara became the leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.48,0:09:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,However, a change began to occur\N in Madara who had been physically fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.57,0:09:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,As I mentioned earlier,\Nthis eye is special.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.45,0:09:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The more you use it, the more it is sealed...\N until you end up with total darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.99,0:10:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the ultimate fate of\Nthe Mangekyo Sharingan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.29,0:10:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The price for gaining power is destroying it yourself,\N losing its light.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.43,0:10:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to regain his sight,\N Madara tried every means possible... yet nothing worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.22,0:10:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,He was in despair.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.29,0:10:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Madara became haunted by\Nthe Mangekyo Sharingan and sought light.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.83,0:10:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.76,0:10:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,He took both eyes from\Nhis younger brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.14,0:11:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Madara now possessed new light.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.56,0:11:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And...never again did the light fade\Nfrom his eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.03,0:11:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,An eternal Mangekyo Sharingan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.33,0:11:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It is said that his younger brother's eyes gained\N eternal light when it found a new host...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.54,0:11:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And it triggered a change.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.42,0:11:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,A new, unique ocular jutsu was born\Nin those eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.26,0:11:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,However, the exchange of eyes can\N only be conducted among clan members.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.09,0:11:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Furthermore, not everyone can attain\Nnew powers from this method.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.10,0:11:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the historical fact that remains\Nafter countless were sacrificed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.27,0:11:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the other secret of this eye...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.40,0:12:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Madara used his power and took control\Nof one ninja clan after another.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.16,0:12:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Ultimately, he formed an alliance with the Senju Clan of the Forest,\N which was known as the strongest ninja clan
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.45,0:12:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and established a new organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.59,0:12:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Later, he clashed with the leader of the Senju Clan,\N the future First Hokage, over the course the village would take.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.05,0:12:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,He lost the battle over leadership,\N but Madara still lives with his ocular powers intact.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.63,0:12:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,He formed a new organization called the\N Akatsuki and hides himself in its shadows.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.39,0:12:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Sixteen years ago, Madara instigated the\N Nine-Tails' attack on Hidden Leaf Village.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.23,0:12:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But that too was stopped by\Nthe Fourth Hokage.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.79,0:12:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,In short...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.83,0:12:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Madara is a bitter, defeated loser...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.92,0:12:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,He is not worthy of becoming\Nthe best among the Uchiha.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.05,0:13:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the one...\N who shall surpass Madara and become the ultimate ninja!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.77,0:13:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And now! I can finally obtain power\Nthat exceeds Madara's!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.06,0:13:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke! You are my new light!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.44,0:13:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You have my spare eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.53,0:13:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Originally, the Uchiha Clan killed off friends\N in order to possess Mangekyo Sharingan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.55,0:13:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Parents and siblings killed each other off\Nto possess eternal ocular powers...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.67,0:13:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And they showed off this power...\NThey are a tainted clan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.89,0:13:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And, from the day you were born,\N you have been inevitably linked to this blood-sullied fate!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.01,0:13:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Now come! My little brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.40,0:13:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall kill you... and free myself from\N this fate and bring about true change!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.27,0:14:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I will be free of the constraints\Nthat bind me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.99,0:14:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But, we only have each other\N{\i1}as siblings.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.83,0:14:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm always going to be there for you,\N {\i1}even if it's only as an obstacle {\i1}for you to overcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.73,0:14:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We are each other's spares!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.19,0:14:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You've been jealous of me\N{\i1}and resented me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.69,0:14:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You've harbored hopes\N{\i1}of surpassing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.74,0:14:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That is why I am allowing you to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.98,0:14:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}For my sake...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.34,0:14:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the true bond between\Nthe brothers of the Uchiha!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.17,0:15:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems...you are finally seeing\Nwhat's inside my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.34,0:15:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So it was all for this...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.93,0:15:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My name is Sasuke Uchiha.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.22,0:15:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There are lots of things I hate.\N{\i1}And not many things I like.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.58,0:15:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Also...I have no intention\N{\i1}of saying I have a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.44,0:15:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I do have ambition!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.64,0:15:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To restore my clan...and kill...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.55,0:15:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}a certain man.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.87,0:15:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I've finally arrived...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.66,0:15:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The moment to fulfill my goal!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.00,0:15:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You say you can see my death...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.66,0:15:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But you cannot win against\Nmy Mangekyo Sharingan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.30,0:15:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, your goal will end\Nas an illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.93,0:15:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you do not possess\Nthe Mangekyo Sharingan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.95,0:16:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're still weak...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.93,0:16:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're weak,\N{\i1}because you don't have enough hate.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.76,0:16:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You can use your eyes all you like,\N but my hate will turn my illusion into reality!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.81,0:16:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Your reality...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.78,0:16:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,is death!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.39,0:17:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even during our shoot out,\N {\i1}he was able to weave signs {\i1}for a Shadow Clone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.18,0:18:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You ran it through with Chidori?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.86,0:19:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me, Sasuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.49,0:19:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my reality...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.27,0:19:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me your light.
